com.iha.emulator.models.value

Interface Value<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of value needed for compilation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractValue, BoilerModeActuatorValue, BoilerStatusSensorValue, BoilerTypeActuatorValue, EmissionsSensorValue, EmptyValue, HumiditySensorValue, LightSensorValue, NoiseSensorValue, OnOffActuatorValue, OnOffSensorValue, OpenClosedSensorValue, PressureSensorValue, TemperatureActuatorValue, TemperatureSensorValue

    public interface Value<T>
    Interface providing method declarations needed to implemented by every value. Also contains enum of existing sensors and actuators, as well as enum with possible generator types.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
